    "Title": "Steal and Slip Away",
    "Description": "We\u2019ve been watching ~mission(Location|Address) for a while. Felt like a primo XenoThreat spot to hit, since there are fewer guards around protecting the goods, but didn\u2019t want to kick down the door until we knew something worthwhile was inside. Well, that glorious day has come.   \n\nGot word that the latest delivery left ~mission(Item) there. We want to get our hands on it, so are looking for someone who can swipe it and then bring it to ~mission(Destination|Address). Sure the forces there won\u2019t make it easy for you, but do this right and try to get out before anyone from the main outpost knows what\u2019s going on.    \n\n- Stows",
